      <title>埃利奥特的目标住友公布股东回报计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/sumitomo-aims-to-bolster-shareholder-returns-in-new-midterm-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本住友商事株式会社表示，将回购股票并采取渐进式股息政策，使其与其他四大同行保持一致，以提高股东回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/sumitomo-aims-to-bolster-shareholder-returns-in-new-midterm-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 05:57:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
